# my implement code
from hw3_code import Hits, PageRank, SimRank

# necessary libraries
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import timeit

# only for visualize graph
import networkx as nx
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
def PlotGraph(Graph):
    maxVertex = np.max(np.asarray(Graph).flatten())
    G = nx.DiGraph()
    G.add_nodes_from([i+1 for i in range(maxVertex)])
    G.add_edges_from(Graph)
    nx.draw(G, with_labels=True, font_color='w', node_color='g', font_size=10)
    plt.show()

def RunAllAlgorithms(f, plotGraph = True, calcSimRank = True, printNonZeroSimRank = True):
    # read data
    print('data: ', f)
    df = pd.read_csv(f, header=None)
    G = df.values
    nVertex = len(set(G.flatten()))

    # plot graph
    if plotGraph:
        print('Graph:')
        PlotGraph(df.values)
        print('========'*6, '\n\n')

    # hits 
    print('Hits: ')
    tic = timeit.default_timer()
    auth, hub = Hits(df.values, print_interation_count=True)
    toc = timeit.default_timer()
    print('wall time: ', toc - tic)
    for i in range(nVertex):
        print('node {}: auth={}, hub={}'.format(i+1, auth[i], hub[i]))
    print('========'*6, '\n\n')


    # PageRank 
    print('PageRank: ')
    tic = timeit.default_timer()
    PR = PageRank(df.values, damping_factor=0.15, print_interation_count=True)
    toc = timeit.default_timer()
    print('wall time: ', toc - tic)
    for i in range(nVertex):
        print('node {}: PageRank={}'.format(i+1, PR[i]))
    print('========'*6, '\n\n')


    # SimRank
    if calcSimRank:
        print('SimRank: ')
        tic = timeit.default_timer()
        simrank = SimRank(df.values, C=0.5, print_interation_count=True)
        toc = timeit.default_timer()
        print('wall time: ', toc - tic)
        print('SimRank Matrix: \n', simrank, '\n')
        print('non-zero simrank: ')
        if printNonZeroSimRank:
            for i in range(nVertex):
                for j in range(nVertex):
                    if simrank[i][j] != 0:
                        print('simrank({}, {}) = {}'.format(i+1, j+1, simrank[i][j]))
        else:
            print('<hidden>. pass printNonZeroSimRank=True parameter to display it.')
        print('========'*6, '\n\n')
